OL,3,CThief murdered Amazon delivery driver
OL,4,Cwith his own van, court told
OL,6,FAn Amazon delivery driver was murdered
OL,7,Fby a thief who ran him over with his
OL,8,Fown van, a court has heard.
OL,10,FClaudiu-Carol Kondor, from Sheffield,
OL,11,Fdied on 20 August last year as he
OL,12,Ftried to prevent his Ford Transit van
OL,13,Fbeing stolen in Leeds.
OL,15,FThe 42-year-old died at the scene in
OL,16,FHeights Drive, Wortley.
OL,18,FA jury at Leeds Crown Court heard Mr
OL,19,FKondor was dragged along the road
OL,20,Fafter becoming caught in the passenger
OL,21,Fdoor as Mark Ross accelerated away.
