OL,3,CThief murdered Amazon delivery driver
OL,4,Cwith his own van, court told
OL,6,FRoss, 32, of Conference Road in
OL,7,FArmley, has admitted manslaughter, but
OL,8,Fdenies murder.
OL,10,FOpening the case, prosecutor John
OL,11,FHarrison KC told the jury Mr Kondor
OL,12,Fwas in the middle of a delivery round
OL,13,Fwhen he saw Ross get into his van.
OL,15,FHe said: "His van contained a large
OL,16,Fnumber of parcels and while he was
OL,17,Fdelivering a parcel and away from his
OL,18,Fvehicle parked on Alliance Street, the
OL,19,Fdefendant climbed into the driver's
OL,20,Fseat intending to drive the van away,
OL,21,Fstealing the van and contents."
