OL,3,CThief murdered Amazon delivery driver
OL,4,Cwith his own van, court told
OL,6,FMr Harrison said Mr Kondor tried to
OL,7,Fstop Ross by opening the passenger
OL,8,Fdoor and climbing in.
OL,10,FHe added: "Unfortunately, it didn't
OL,11,Fprevent the defendant from driving
OL,12,Faway, with Mr Kondor holding onto the
OL,13,Fpassenger door.
OL,15,F"It appears Mr Kondor, did not wish
OL,16,Fto, or perhaps could not let go of his
OL,17,Fvan, but he did not want the defendant
OL,18,Fto steal."
