OL,3,CThief murdered Amazon delivery driver
OL,4,Cwith his own van, court told
OL,6,FThe court heard Ross drove at speeds
OL,7,Fof up to 60mph with Mr Kondor holding
OL,8,Fon. The van collided with a parked car.
OL,10,FThe court was told that Ross claims he
OL,11,Fwas unaware Mr Kondor was holding onto
OL,12,Fthe van.
