OL,3,CThief murdered Amazon delivery driver
OL,4,Cwith his own van, court told
OL,6,FMr Harrison said: "The prosecution's
OL,7,Fcase is he must have known he was
OL,8,Fhanging on because the door was open
OL,9,Fand it must have been obvious the door
OL,10,Fwas open and Mr Kondor was there. Why
OL,11,Fdid the defendant drive so quickly and
OL,12,Ferratically, weaving side to side
OL,13,Funless he was trying to dislodge the
OL,14,Fpassenger?
OL,16,F"He deliberately drove the side of the
OL,17,Fvan into collision."
OL,19,FMr Kondor suffered fatal head and
OL,20,Fchest injuries in a second collision
OL,21,Fwith a parked car.
