OL,3,CThief murdered Amazon delivery driver
OL,4,Cwith his own van, court told
OL,6,FMr Harrison added: "It is the
OL,7,Fprosecution's case that the defendant
OL,8,Fmurdered Mr Kondor by driving at
OL,9,Fexcessive speed or driving to
OL,10,Fcollision with a parked car to either
OL,11,Fkill him or cause really serious harm."
OL,13,FDuring the opening, the court was
OL,14,Fshown footage of the van being driven
OL,15,Fby Ross in Wingate Road. Mr Kondor can
OL,16,Fbe seen hanging onto the side of the
OL,17,Fvan.
